Package: sacADos
Type: Package
Title: Discrete Optimisation for Feature Selection: the 0-1 Knapsack Problem in R and Rcpp
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-06-03
Author: Mahir Dursunoglu
Maintainer: Mahir Dursunoglu <mahir.dursunoglu@mindlapse.ai>
Description: Implementations of the 0-1 knapsack problem applied to feature
    selection under a resource budget. Provides a naive exhaustive search and a
    dynamic-programming solver in R and Rcpp, a self-tuning online heuristic
    (knapsack_adaptive) in R and Rcpp, and an LP upper bound for gap certification.
    Also provides instance generators for the four Pisinger weight/value families
    used to benchmark the algorithms.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.5)
Suggests:
